'''Vericut'''（通常拼写为 '''VERICUT'''），是一款用于模拟[[机床加工|机床加工]]的[[仿真|仿真]][[软件|软件]]。它通常用于模拟[[数控机床|机床刀具运动]]以及加工时材料去除过程，检测加工过程中可能出现的错误或数控加工程序中的错误。<ref name="MMTLineofDefense">{{cite news | last =Baranek | first =Sherry L. | coauthors = | title =A Final Line of Defense to Making a Quality Program and Product | newspaper =Moldmaking Technology | location = | pages = | language = | publisher =HighBeam | date =1 May 2013 | url =http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-330680610.html | accessdate =3 December 2013 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150329112224/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-330680610.html | archive-date =2015-03-29 | dead-url =yes }}</ref>它由CGTech公司所开发<ref name="VericutGCorps"/>，并且在1988年发布了第一个版本。

==历史==
Vericut在1988年由CGTech公司所设计，<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview">{{cite news | last =Huang | first =Pel | coauthors = | title =Leading the Manufacturing Simulation technology | newspaper =Eworks Global | location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date =4 May 2009 | url =http://www.eworksglobal.com/reports_128858991954531250.htm | accessdate =3 December 2013 | archive-date =2019-09-11 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20190911070257/http://www.eworksglobal.com/reports_128858991954531250.htm }}</ref> 软件最初设计运行于 [[Unix|Unix]]系统，后来扩展至 [[个人电脑|个人电脑]], [[惠普|惠普]], [[IBM兼容机|IBM兼容机]], [[DEC|DEC工作站]]以及其他计算机。<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview"/> Vericut一开始就被安装和应用与[[世界500强|世界500强]]和其他知名公司包括[[波音|波音]] ,<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview"/> [[空中巴士|空中巴士]],<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview"/> [[通用汽车|通用汽车]],<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview"/> 和 [[以色列航太工业|以色列航太工业]]。<ref>{{cite news| last =| first =| coauthors =| title =Makit completes IAI Vericut installation| newspaper =Israel Business Today| location =| pages =| language =| publisher =HighBeam| date =25 September 1996| url =http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-18760463.html| accessdate =2 December 2013| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150329112228/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-18760463.html| archive-date =2015-03-29| dead-url =yes}}</ref>直到2009年, Vericut在全世界范围内以被超过2000家公司所应用。<ref name="EworksGLobalLeadInterview"/> 在2011年, 以销售收入计算，CGTech公司已经成为最大的独立数控验证与仿真软件供应商，共计超过9000份软件拷贝被安装使用.<ref>{{cite news | last = | first = | coauthors = | title =NC Market Analysis Report – Version 21 | newspaper =CIM 2012 Market Analysis Report | location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date =2012 | url = | accessdate = }}</ref>

==特点==

Vericut通常作为一个单独运行的软件，但也可以集成入[[计算机辅助设计|CAD]], [[计算机辅助制造|CAM]], 和 [[PL/M|PLM系统]]包括 [[CATIA|CATIA]], [[NX_(Unigraphics)|Siemens NX]], [[PowerMILL|PowerMILL]], [[Vero_Software|EdgeCAM]], [[Mastercam|Mastercam]] and [[List_of_CAx_companies|hyperMILL]].<ref>{{cite web | last = | first = | authorlink = | coauthors = | title =CGTech | work = | publisher =The Engineer | date = | url =http://source.theengineer.co.uk/cgtech/9897.supplier | format = | doi = | accessdate =22 November 2013 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20141231141957/http://source.theengineer.co.uk/cgtech/9897.supplier | archive-date =2014-12-31 | dead-url =yes }}</ref> 通过模拟3至5轴的运动来模拟磨削与钻孔操作。<ref name="TandPOneOff">{{cite news| last =| first =| coauthors =| title =Verify one-off programs without cutting metal| newspaper =Tooling & Production| location =| pages =| language =| publisher =HighBeam| date =1 February 1992| url =http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-12031209.html| accessdate =22 November 2013| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150329112222/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-12031209.html| archive-date =2015-03-29| dead-url =yes}}</ref> 整个模拟仿真的过程以3维图像的形式显示了将原料依据预定义的数控加工程序加工成零件的过程<ref name="LearningNCwiout">{{cite news| last =| first =| coauthors =| title =Learning NC without machines| newspaper =Tooling & Production| location =| pages =| language =| publisher =HighBeam| date =1 April 1993| url =http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-14123107.html| accessdate =22 November 2013| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150329112226/http://www.highbeam.com/doc/1G1-14123107.html| archive-date =2015-03-29| dead-url =yes}}</ref>
===机床仿真===

Vericut能够实现客制化并且包含了一些经过挑选的数控机床。机床模型也能够利用CAD系统或者类似的软件从零开始搭建。<ref name="MMTLineofDefense"/> 它包含了一个组件数来管理机床的运动。<ref>{{cite journal | last =Pei | first =Liu | authorlink = | coauthors = | title =Virtual Machining Technology Based on UG and Vericut | journal =[[Advanced_Materials|Advanced Materials]] | volume =452-453 | issue = | pages = | publisher =Scientific.net | location = | date =January 2012 | language = | url =http://www.scientific.net/AMR.452-453.1267 | jstor = | issn = | doi =10.4028/www.scientific.net/AMR.452-453.1267 | id = | mr = | zbl = | jfm = | accessdate =3 December 2013 | archive-date =2018-06-02 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20180602002147/https://www.scientific.net/AMR.452-453.1267 }}</ref> Vericut模拟机床的全部特征就如同它们在车间里那样并且能够在工件层面展示材料的去除过程。<ref name="LearningNCwiout"/> 它也能够模拟数控机床的控制以及自动检测可能的碰撞和机床的超程，以此能够降低机床损坏的可能性。<ref name="EnegeryPartysAustrailia">{{cite news | last =Lorincz | first =Jim | coauthors = | title =Energy parts are complex and big | newspaper =Australian Manufacturing Technology| location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date =May 2010 | url = | accessdate = }}</ref><ref name="MMTLineofDefense"/> 

在机床仿真方面的一个特点，能够检测所有机床部件之间可能存在的由于近距离接触造成的事故以及碰撞。<!--翻译的不准确，请高手参照原文重新润饰，原文：The machine simulation feature detects all machine components for near-misses and collisions.--><ref name="TandPOneOff"/> 易发生近距离接触区域能够被用户在组件树相关部分进行设置，以此来检测由于近距离可能造成的错误和超程错误。<!--翻译的不准确，请高手参照原文重新润饰，原文：Near miss zones can be set up by users around components to check for close calls and over-travel errors.--><ref name="TandPOneOff"/> 机床运动的仿真画面能够在回放模式快进或回放。<ref>{{cite news | last =Richardson | first =Mike | coauthors = | title =CGTech launches latest Vericut CNC  software | newspaper =Aerospace Magazine | location = | pages = | language = | publisher = | date =20 April 2011 | url =http://www.aero-mag.com/news/20114/854/ | accessdate =2 December 2013 | archive-date =2016-03-04 | archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160304004009/http://www.aero-mag.com/news/20114/854/ }}</ref>

===数控程序优化===

Vericut具有数控程序优化的功能。它能够基于预先编制的程序所规定的轴速自动为每一次切割检测{{link-en|安全轴速|Speeds and feeds}}，减少循环时间。 这种优化据称能够减少因加工出错而废弃的成型零件数量，工具的破损以及刀具偏差。<ref name="EnegeryPartysAustrailia"/>

